text: Anatoly Zaytsev (born 9 January 1947) is a Soviet skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tomsk
